sRGB: sRGB / Rec709 (BT.709) color primaries, with D65 white point.
Rec2020: Rec2020 (BT.2020) primaries with D65 white point.
ACESAP0: ACES AP0 wide gamut primaries, with D60 white point.
ACESAP1: ACES AP1 / ACEScg wide gamut primaries, with D60 white point.
P3DCI: P3 (Theater) primaries, with DCI Calibration white point.
P3D65: P3 (Display) primaries, with D65 white point.
Custom: User defined color space and white point.
